    <text>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_c5442680">
            <hi rendition="#c">
                <head>
                    <lb />The<lb />Welte Mignon Studios </head>
                <lb />Offer you exceptional
                opportunities </hi>
        </div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_a6014ae2">
            <lb />
            <hi rendition="#u">
                The Master Himself
            </hi>
        </div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_b536deda">
            <lb />Not just mechanical playing of his compositions,<lb />but <seg ana="#physical_presence" type="topic" resp="#np">his own fingers on your
            keyboard</seg>.</div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_e56f4d74">
            <lb />
            <hi rendition="#u">
                <seg type="topic" ana="#touch_of_a_button" resp="#np">At Your Command</seg>
            </hi>
        </div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_2389efb5">
            <lb />Accept as soon as you can our cordial invita-<lb />tion to spend a delightful hour
            or two with<lb />the masters of classic or popular music at our<lb />beautiful studios.
            We shall gladly play your fav-<lb />orite selections. We shall place at your disposal
            the<lb />services of a staff of musicians whose advice is al-<lb />ways ready but is
            never intruded. We offer a re-<lb />markable collection of instruments at reasonable<lb />prices
            and on exceptional terms.</div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_2cbb468e">
            <lb />If <persName corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/118986724">Paderewski</persName>
            played to you, on your own piano, ex-<lb />actly as he played at the very zenith of his
            career when<lb />those marvelous fingers performed miracles, you could<lb />count it a
            great event in your life. This is what the<lb />WELTE MIGNON Reproducing Piano will do
            for you.<lb /><persName corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/118986724">Paderewski</persName>
            <seg ana="#soulfulness" type="topic" resp="#np">played his soul into the Welte</seg>,
            <seg ana="#immortality" type="topic" resp="#np">knowing<lb />full well that thus could he better pass on
            to coming gen-<lb />erations the perfect expression of his genius</seg>. It is the
            <seg ana="#soulfulness" type="topic" resp="#np">soul-<lb />expression</seg>
            that 
            <seg ana="#listening" type="topic" resp="#np">you feel when you listen to the Welte</seg>;
            and<lb />
            <seg ana="#repeatability" resp="#np" type="topic">
                you may hear it not only once, but
                as often as you wish.
            </seg>
            <lb /><persName corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/118986724">
            Paderewski</persName>,
            <persName corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/124379923">Lhevinne</persName>,
            <persName corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/11918625X">Hofmann</persName>,
            <persName corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/116014490">de Pachman</persName>,
            <persName corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/118518011">Busoni</persName>
            ,
            <persName corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/11875081X">Saint-<lb />Saens</persName>,
            <persName corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/118697641">Grieg</persName>,
            <persName corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/118501437">d'Albert</persName>–156
            masters in all have
            <seg ana="#soulfulness" type="topic" resp="#np">
                played into the Welte<lb />for you the very essence of their musical
                personalities
            </seg>,
            <seg ana="#distinction_from_mechanical">
                for Welte re-<lb />production is not "stencil cutting,"
            </seg> but
            <seg ana="#exact_reproduction" resp="#np" type="topic">
                absolute tonal duplication.
            </seg>
            <lb />There are over 5,000 record-rolls in the Welte repertoire. Come<lb />in
            to-day and hear your favorites. And bear in mind that the Welte<lb />is within your
            means, for it is sold on terms–your own within reason.</div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_80803b8a">
            <lb />Our stock includes many examples of fine standard<lb />makes–
            <orgName>Welte</orgName>, <orgName>Estey</orgName>, <orgName>Conway</orgName>,
            and others–shown in a<lb />variety of case-designs and woods, giving you ample op-<lb />portunity
            to find the instrument that exactly suits your<lb />taste and means. We sell all grades
            (except "cheap").<lb />You can buy from us a really good instrument as low as<lb />$450,
            on a series of monthly payments–terms, your own<lb />within reason.</div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_b3e47c4c">
            <lb />Pianos and<lb />Player-Pianos<lb />at the Prices<lb />You expect<lb />to Pay</div>
            <div facs="#eSc_textblock_53814f97">
                <lb />WELTE TERMS</div>
            <div facs="#eSc_textblock_e007686d">
            <lb />We maintain that if music is to be<lb />enjoyed by everyone, it must be with<lb />in
            everyone's reach. So we placed<lb />every instrument in the Welte<lb />Mignon Studios
            just there–within<lb />EVERYONE'S means. Pick out any<lb />instrument you like, from
            lowest to highest price, and buy<lb />it on terms that are practically your own.</div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_cd6fbfd8">
            <lb />A wonderful showing of Phonographs</div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_4ba7b7ec">
            <lb />VICTROLAS</div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_3c860cc6">
            <lb />In our Victor department are all the latest<lb />designs of this standard talking
            machine<lb />as well as a complete stock of the new<lb />records. You will find no
            pleasanter sur-<lb />roundings in which to listen to your favorite<lb />music<lb />Visitors
            at Welte Mignon Studios are not<lb />importuned to buy, but when you do buy<lb />you
            find prices no higher than elsewhere.<lb />Our terms are your own within reason.</div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_c69c9e23">
            <lb />A unique department, stocket with the<lb />famous Pathe models in beautiful cases,<lb />some
            in period designs–Sheraton, William<lb />and mary, Jacobean, Louis XV and others<lb />–at
            a wide range of prices. Each instru-<lb />ment fitted with the famous Pathe sapphire<lb />ball
            reproducer, giving unsurpassed velvety<lb />sweetness and clearness of tone, and requir-<lb />ing
            no change of needle. Let us play Pathe<lb />for you. Terms your own within reason.</div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_3838333f">
            <lb />PATHE</div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_86963cd3">
            <lb />All the new Victor Records and Pathe<lb />Discs may be heard here as soon as they<lb />are
            published. Late "jazz" tunes, popular<lb />hits from current shows, the melodies every-<lb />one
            whistles and dances to, and those finer<lb />things constantly being recorded by great<lb />singers
            and instrumentalists. Learn to re-<lb />gard the Welte Mignon Studios as your<lb />place
            for hearing records. Drop in when-<lb />over you are "up the Avenue."</div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_17b7db97">
            <lb />
            <hi rendition="#c">
                <hi rendition="#u">
                    <hi rendition="#i">
                        Can you drop in at once?
                    </hi>
                </hi>
            </hi>

            <lb />No matter how many times you've visited the Studios before this,<lb />come in
            again; there's always something new to see and to hear. Re-<lb />member that you are
            never pressed to buy–just come in as you would<lb />visit a famous picture gallery. But
            if you cannot come today or to-<lb />morrow; at least, send this coupon by way of
            getting information on<lb />the latest instrument designs.</div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_d659d9d8">
            <lb />RECORDS</div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_0eb08447">
            <lb />The<lb />Welte Mignon Studios</div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_90b895ae">
            <lb />6667 Fifth Avenue</div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_d72e074e">
            <lb />The Welte Mignon Studios,<lb />667 Fifth Ave., New York.<lb />Without any
            obligation to me, send com-<lb />plete information on the items checked:<lb />Pianos<lb />Reproducing
            Pianos<lb />Player Pianos<lb />Victor<lb />Pathe<lb />Name<lb />Address<lb />Sun-Harald,
            4-30.</div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_332b9320">
            <lb />At 53rd Street</div>
